: Research Nigerian Search Intent\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"41\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      Before you touch a meta tag, you need to understand how Nigerians phrase their searches. \\\\\\\"Cheap web design\\\\\\\" vs \\\\\\\"affordable website design Nigeria\\\\\\\" � the second converts at 4� the rate. Use Google's autocomplete on a Nigerian IP address, and mine Google Search Console for actual query data from Nigerian users.\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"42\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      Step 2: Fix Your Technical Foundation\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"43\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      A site that loads in 8 seconds on 3G will never rank for competitive Nigerian terms � because it will never retain users long enough to generate the engagement signals Google needs. Target LCP under 2.5 seconds on a simulated 4G connection. This alone eliminates 80% of your Nigerian competitors.\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"44\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      Step 3: Establish Local Signals\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"45\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"      Your Google Business Profile, consistent NAP citations across Nigerian directories (VConnect, BusinessList Nigeria), and location-specific landing pages are non-negotiable for local SEO dominance. Add LocalBusiness schema markup to every relevant page.\\\\r\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"br\\\",\\\"46\\\",{}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"47\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"        Pro Tip: Create city-specific service pages for your top 5 Nigerian city markets. \\\\\\\"Web design Lagos\\\\\\\" and \\\\\\\"web design Abuja\\\\\\\" are completely different search opportunities � and most agencies serve them from a single page.\\\\r\\\"}],\\\"$L1e\\\",\\\"$L1f\\\",\\\"$L20\\\",\\\"$L21\\\",\\\"$L22\\\",\\\"$L23\\\",\\\"$L24\\\",\\\"$